"DEEP MINES"

Deep Mines (Empire ability)

Mines you dig or prospect will have roughly 50% more ore. You must be the first
player to build a mine or prospect on a given mountain tile (at least, since
the last mountain reset), otherwise your deep mines ability will have no effect.

Once you have started a mine (or prospected) a given mountain tile, it will
remain a deep mine unless the mountain is reset at the end of the year. For
more information on mountain resets, see HELP MINE.

See also: MINE, PROSPECT, RARE METALS
